  <brief_title>Fluvastatin Versus Hepatitis C Virus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Dose Finding Study of Fluvastatin for in Vivo Demonstration of Inhibiting Hepatitis C Replication in Patients Infected With Chronic Hepatitis C With Special Attention to the African-American Population.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
