  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a dose finding and efficacy trial for fluvastatin versus hepatitis C.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Four different oral doses of fluvastatin will be used for 14 days and the viral load of
      hepatitis C will be measured weekly. This has been extended to different doses for 9-12
      weeks.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
